    <para id="import-auto-id2743296">4. Substitute the known values into the equation and solve for <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>N</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. </para>
    <equation id="import-auto-id2887530"><m:math>
        
